OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine, then
OL,7,Fdry overnight with clear spells and
OL,8,Fpatchy cloud. Another chilly night
OL,9,Fwith some frost possible in the
OL,10,Fcountryside. Easterly winds freshening
OL,11,Fover higher ground and on exposed
OL,12,Fcoasts, keeping it milder here.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA good deal of cloud with
OL,15,Fsome sunshine, this hazy at times,
OL,16,Fespecially in the west. Windy in
OL,17,Fplaces with strengthening easterly
OL,18,Fwinds, but feeling pleasant out of the
OL,19,Fwind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
