OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FStrong
OL,6,Feasterly winds on Wednesday with gales
OL,7,Fpossible on exposed coasts. Showers
OL,8,Fpossible in the west, sunnier in the
OL,9,Feast. Mostly fine thereafter though
OL,10,Fstill breezy in places. Turning warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
